1. *Čist* mi je stan. (My apartment is clean.) 
2. On je *čist* čovek. (He is an honest man.) 
3. Sve je *čisto* u sobi. (Everything is clean in the room.) 
4. *Čistim* zube svaki dan. (I brush my teeth every day.) 
5. Ona je *čista* devojka. (She is a pure girl.) 
6. *Čistačica* je obrisala prašinu. (The cleaner wiped the dust.)